lead_paragraph: Pat Cummins' international career has had more than its fair share of false starts due to injuries but captain Steve Smith hopes the upcoming one-day series against New Zealand will prove a launchpad for the Australia fast bowler to kick on.

headline.print_headline: Australia's Cummins to Make Latest Comeback in One-Dayers
